Nike Dunk Low College Navy Grey (W)
results.story: The women's Nike Dunk Low SP ‘College Navy’ delivers a two-tone colorway of the retro hoops shoe originally released in 1985. The all-leather upper combines a navy blue base with contrasting overlays in Wolf Grey. An unexpected pop of color arrives via Nike branding in University Red on the heel tab and woven tongue tag, while satin laces and a matching collar lining add to the shoe’s luxe look. A translucent rubber outsole offers grippy traction underfoot.

Nike Dunk Low Medium Curry
results.story: The Nike Dunk Low Premium ‘Medium Curry’ dresses the retro silhouette in a suede upper finished in warm, autumnal hues. A cream-hued base is contrasted by curry brown overlays at the toe and heel, while Fossil coloring is applied to the Swoosh and heel tab, the latter marked with traditional Nike branding. The low-top rides on a durable rubber cupsole, featuring a grippy traction pattern virtually identical to another mid ‘80s hoops shoe, the Air Jordan 1.

Nike Air Max 1 Clot Kiss of Death (2021)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the CLOT x Nike Air Max 1 ‘Kiss of Death’ revives a fan-favorite collaborative colorway initially released in 2006. Like the original, the retro runner is marked by a deconstructed tan suede upper with transparent paneling on the toe box and a scaly texture on the Swoosh. The heel overlay undergoes a color flip, featuring an orange CLOT logo against a red backdrop while the translucent rubber outsole reveals a reflexology-inspired graphic in a new multicolor design.

results.name: CLOT x Air Max 1 PS 'Kiss of Death' 2021
results.story: Built for little kids, the 2021 reissue of the CLOT x Nike Air Max 1 PS ‘Kiss of Death’ brings back a coveted collaboration from 2006 — the first ever joint effort between the Swoosh and Edison Chen’s streetwear brand. Updated with refreshed details, the sneaker’s standout features remain intact, including a transparent toe box, scaly red leather Swoosh and deconstructed ostrich-skin collar. They’re joined by a reflective heel overlay in red leather, along with upgraded reflexology-inspired graphics on the custom sockliner and translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Nike Air Max 1 clot Kiss of Death CHA
results.story: The CLOT x Nike Air Max 1 ‘Kiss of Death CHA’ delivers a play on the original collaboration between the Swoosh and Edison Chen’s streetwear brand. While the older shoe was inspired by reflexology, its successor takes its design cues from tea, deemed by CLOT as one of the necessities of Chinese life. The original’s defining attributes remain unchanged, including a clear toe box, deconstructed collar and translucent rubber outsole, the latter marked with a familiar pressure-point graphic. The suede upper is rendered in tan and brown paneling with a red leather Swoosh. The same crimson hue is repeated on CLOT branding embroidered on the heel overlay.

results.name: Court Borough Low PS 'White Deep Royal'
Nike Air Max 90 NRG Bacon (2021)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the DQM x Nike Air Max 90 ‘Bacon’ brings back the coveted colorway originally released in 2004 as a collaboration with Dave’s Quality Meat. The shoe’s distinctive palette, featuring an off-white leather base with red suede overlays, a pink leather Swoosh and brown TPU accents, is intended to evoke the look of strips of bacon. The concept reflected the unique butcher shop aesthetic of the legendary NYC sneaker boutique founded in 2003 by Dave Ortiz and Chris Keefe.

Nike Air Max Pre-Day Light Liquid Lime
results.story: Releasing as part of the brand’s 2021 Air Max Day celebration, the Nike Air Max Pre-Day ‘Liquid Lime’ delivers a new addition to the Air Max family, one that carries the torch for previous generations of the vaunted sneaker line. The sneaker’s retro aesthetic is bound up in a sustainable build, comprising a bright green textile upper made from 100% recycled polyester, and a black rubber outsole built with at least 13% Nike Grind Rubber. The shoe’s standout feature is the visible Air sole unit in the heel, unchanged from the one used in the Air Max 1 and 90, but fully exposed and not viewed through an enclosed window.

results.name: Nike Air Max 1 Evolution Of Icons
results.story: Launching as part of the brand’s 2021 Air Max Day festivities, the Nike Air Max 1 ‘Evolution of Icons’ features a unique design that incorporates familiar details from different Air Max models. The sneaker wears a white leather upper with mismatched Swooshes drawn from the likes of the ‘Neon’ Air Max 95 and ‘Dusty Cactus’ Air Max 93. Molded eyelets are taken from the 90, toe box embroidery references the ‘98, and a gradient grey mudguard offers a further nod to the 95. ‘3.26,’ aka Air Max Day, is debossed on the left heel, while the insole’s timeline graphic depicts the various silhouettes that make up the shoe’s hybrid composition.

React Gato 'Grey Fog Bright Crimson'
results.story: The Nike React Gato ‘Grey Fog Bright Crimson’ showcases vibrant accents on an indoor soccer shoe that offers game-ready control and responsiveness. The grey Flyknit upper is fused and molded with a durable compound for improved touch, while a reinforced band around the toe provides added durability. The low-profile silhouette rides on a full-length Nike React midsole, supported by a marbled red rubber outsole fitted with circular pods for enhanced feel.

results.name: Nike Air Max 97 Swarovski Polar Blue (W)
results.story: The Swarovski x Nike women’s Air Max 97 ‘Polar Blue’ offers a luxe take on an OG colorway of the retro runner. The sneaker makes use of a silver mesh upper with fused overlays encrusted with tiny Swarovski crystals, adding shimmer to the sneaker’s water ripple-inspired lines. A pale blue mini-Swoosh adorns the lateral quarter panel and oval tongue patch. Buoyant cushioning arrives via a polyurethane midsole, fitted with a historic full-length Max Air unit.

results.name: Air Zoom Terra Kiger 7 'Black Pure Platinum'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Terra Kiger 7 ‘Black Pure Platinum’ highlights neutral tones on a running shoe built to handle rugged terrain. Breathable black mesh is utilized on the upper, featuring synthetic no-sew overlays and a Dynamic Fit System for midfoot lockdown. The Nike React midsole houses an encapsulated Zoom Air unit in the forefoot for extra-responsive cushioning. Underfoot, the rubber outsole is equipped multidirectional traction lugs for superior grip.

results.name: Heritage Vulc SB 'Coast Psychic Blue'
results.story: The Nike Heritage Vulc SB ‘Coast Psychic Blue’ highlights two shades of blue on a streamlined skate shoe crafted from suede with washed canvas quarter panels. A Nike wordmark is embroidered in white lettering on the heel tab, matched by signature Swoosh branding in white leather. A retro exposed-foam tongue combines with a cushy sockliner for a comfortable fit. A gum rubber cupsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

results.name: Air Max 2090 SE GS 'Dark Purple Dust'
Wmns Offcourt Duo Slide 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Offcourt Duo Slide ‘Black White’ delivers a premium take on the classic slide. The upper is composed of two black synthetic leather straps, both lined in 100% recycled fabric and the wider of the two stamped with a contrasting white Nike wordmark. A micro-texture on the Revive foam footbed is designed for non-slip comfort. A lightweight EVA outsole features a circular traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Crimson Bliss Metallic Platinum’ delivers a versatile silhouette that can be slipped easily on and off, thanks to a laceless mesh upper with webbing pull tabs at the tongue and heel. The sneaker’s warm coral hue is offset by a metallic silver Swoosh that adorns a supportive midfoot cage. The lightweight build is supported by a cushy foam sole unit, featuring flex grooves underfoot that promote a smooth, natural stride.

results.name: Wmns Blazer Low '77 'Triple White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Blazer Low ‘77 ‘Triple White’ treats the vintage hoops shoe to a pristine blank-slate finish. The upper is constructed from crisp white leather and branded with a matching white retro Swoosh, along with an embossed Nike wordmark on the heel tab. The tonal theme continues on a woven tag atop a vintage exposed-foam tongue. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a classic herringbone traction pattern originally designed for the hardwood.

results.name: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Light Smoke Grey
Canyon Sandal 'Cargo Khaki'
results.story: The Nike Canyon Sandal ‘Cargo Khaki’ projects an ACG-inspired aesthetic, highlighted by a rugged build finished in a contrasting blend of earth tones and vibrant accents. The upper utilizes triple-strap closure for a secure, custom fit, while a dual-density foam midsole offers lightweight cushioning with every step. The contoured outsole features deep flex grooves and a traction pattern modeled after Nike’s classic waffle tread. Rubber under the toe and heel provides added durability.

results.name: Wmns Lavante Terrain 'Black Ceramic Pink'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Lavante Terrain ‘Black Ceramic Pink’ highlights a simple two-tone finish on a versatile running shoe built to handle off-road use. Breathable black mesh on the upper is fortified with tonal synthetic leather overlays and accented with contrasting pink side stripes. Responsive cushioning arrives via a full-length FuelFoam midsole, supported by a high-traction rubber outsole that offers reliable grip through all conditions.

results.name: Zoom Blazer Mid SB 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike Zoom Blazer Mid SB ‘Black White’ floods the exterior of the retro silhouette with a stark one-note finish, save for the signature branding element that adorns each of the side panels. The sneaker’s retro Swoosh stands out in white suede against a pitch-black backdrop, also constructed from suede and embellished with tonal stitch detailing. Performance benefits include a springy Zoom Air unit in the sockliner and a grippy herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Air Max Bella TR 4 'White Green Glow'
Killshot OG 'Sail Oil Green'
results.story: The Nike Killshot OG ‘Sail Oil Green’ showcases an elemental two-tone palette on a lifestyle silhouette modeled after the vintage tennis shoe from 1979. Equipped with the plush exposed-foam tongue of the original, the low-top carries a breathable off-white mesh upper with tonal suede overlays at the toe and heel. Contrasting olive green accents land on the retro leather Swoosh and Nike-branded heel tab. A durable rubber cupsole anchors the throwback silhouette.

results.name: Court Legacy Print 'Tie-Dye'
results.story: The Nike Court Legacy Print ‘Tie-Dye’ features slip-on construction on a low-top silhouette that channels vintage tennis style. A blue tie-dye print suffuses the breathable canvas upper, lined in synthetic leather and equipped with elastic gore panels for easy on and off. The sneaker rides on a vulcanized rubber midsole with pinstripe detailing and a Swoosh-branded license plate at the heel. Underfoot, a herringbone-tread gum rubber outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Light Violet (GS)
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Blazer Mid ‘77 Suede GS ‘Light Violet’ makes over the retro silhouette with a monochromatic pastel finish throughout the suede upper. The pale lavender hue extends to the laces, retro leather Swoosh and Nike-branded heel tab. Contrasting colors are confined to the woven tongue tag, featuring a standard Nike wordmark and an orange Swoosh. The sneaker’s traditional autoclave tooling comes complete with a standard herringbone tread.

results.name: Vapor Edge Elite 360 Flyknit 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike Vapor Edge Elite 360 Flyknit ‘Black White’ showcases a gradient finish on a football cleat engineered for lightweight speed. The sock-like upper is crafted from 360-degree Flyknit and overlaid with protective NikeSkin. A toggle ghost lacing system provides a secure fit, while an elastic cuff combines with a webbing pull tab to deliver easy on and off. An internal full-length plate yields flexible support. Underfoot, widely placed studs offer superior grip.

results.name: React Vision '3M Pack' By You
results.story: Created via the brand’s customization service, the Nike React Vision ‘3M Pack’ By You carries a textile upper lined in Thinsulate. Reflective Scotchlite detailing on the sneaker’s no-sew heel overlay and distinctive patchwork eyestays offer added visibility in low-light conditions. A woven 3M tag on the heel of the right shoe can be left intact or torn away. The sneaker rides on a plush React foam midsole, reinforced underfoot with rubber pods for enhanced durability and traction.

results.name: Nike Air Max 97 Leopard (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Air Max 97 ‘Leopard’ features a unique design that blends twin inspirations drawn from the natural world. In addition to the sneaker’s wavy overlays, treated to a reflective finish and designed to mimic a water ripple effect, the textile and suede upper is covered in an all-over graphic made up of numerous leopard spots. Mini Swooshes in Peach Cream offer contrasting pops of color. The sneaker is mounted on a polyurethane midsole with full-length Max Air cushioning.

results.name: Air Zoom Victory Tour 2 'White Metallic Platinum'
results.story: The Nike Air Zoom Victory Tour 2 ‘White Metallic Platinum’ makes use of a one-piece full-grain leather upper, treated to a water-proof coating and equipped with a foam padded collar. Responsive cushioning arrives via a Zoom Air unit stitched directly to the upper, supported by a full-length plate for improved energy return. Nike React foam under the heel adds to the shoe’s cushioned comfort. The hybrid outsole combines integrated traction with seven removable spikes for exceptional grip.

results.name: Revolution 5 SE PS 'Crimson Tint Multi'
results.story: The Nike Revolution 5 SE PS ‘Crimson Tint Multi’ highlights a pastel finish on a versatile sneaker designed for little kids. Elastic no-tie laces combine with a webbing pull tab and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap to provide easy on and off. The upper, constructed from peach-colored knit textile and accented with a color-fade Swoosh, rides on a plush foam midsole. Underfoot, a full-length rubber outsole in Glacier Blue offers durable traction.

results.name: MD Valiant GS 'White Multi'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike MD Valiant GS ‘White Multi’ highlights a limited spectrum of pastel accents on a casual sneaker inspired by ‘80s running style. The upper is constructed from white textile with tonal synthetic leather overlays at the toe and heel. The signature Swoosh is rendered in a gradient blend of yellow, blue and pink hues, a color combination that’s repeated on the Nike logo that adorns the iridescent heel tab. A waffle-traction rubber outsole delivers an additional nod to Nike heritage.
